  <title>GDK-Pixbuf-&gdk-pixbuf-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The GDK-Pixbuf is a toolkit for image loading and pixel buffer
      manipulation.
    </para>

